Class MoveableObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • game2D.objects.GameObject
      • game2D.objects.MoveableObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bullet, Enemy, PlayerShip, Pop, PowerUp

    public abstract class MoveableObject
extends GameObject
    Moving objects in the game. The movement is controlled by Motion object. They have speed, strength, health and weapon too.
    Author:
    Fudou
